        </linklist>
        <comment>IL-12 receptor beta 2 is a subchain of the IL-12 receptor.

We assume that IL12RB2 is inhibited by Stat6 in order to reproduce the inhibition of IL12RB2 expression by IL4 (Szabo et al., 1997, Fig.1).</comment>
